                        <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18430821-2591-offence-1 t18430821-cd-317"></join>25th of July</rs>, 1152 pipes, value 12<hi rend="italic">s</hi>.; and 1 basket, 2<hi rend="italic">s</hi>.; the goods of <persName id="t18430821-name-1871" type="victimName">
